data.description: Price reduced, seeking offers.  Take advantage of this rare opportunity in one of the most desirable neighborhoods from Seminole to Clearwater.   This 4-bedroom, 2½ bath family home has an oversized 24x30 garage on nearly one quarter acre with a side entrance and land enough for a pool +  RV and boat.  All the big-ticket items have been replaced from the stainless appliances to the AC in 2019, the roof in 2020 and most recently…the water heater and hurricane rated windows at a cost of $38,000.  The first floor is wide open from the kitchen and dining area to the 18 x 13 family room with French doors that lead out to the patio.  Also on the first floor is the 18x13 living room with a study that’s currently being used as a 5th bedroom. Flooring allowance or help with closing costs with an acceptable offer. In the past year only 2 homes have come up for sale in Bay Hills and none for under $670,000.  Choose your flooring and colors and take this phenomenal opportunity to the next level…
